data.description: Seller is now offering up to $3,000 credit toward closing costs! This charming home features 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, making it perfect for a small family, or individuals seeking a cozy living space to call home. The interior has been freshly painted, giving it a fresh and updated look. Additionally, the home boasts laminate floors throughout the majority of the home and an updated bathroom, that's worth a look! For added convenience and security, the property is equipped with a Nest smart learning thermostat and a smart lock on the front door. Great price, just a short commute to Stewart elementary school! Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely home yours.
